                                <p>
                                    Once the student locates the Exam Center, they need to verify their mobile number on Million Lights website and proceed to buy a voucher Code.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-1 col-md-2"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-10 col-md-8 sepration" id="sepration3" hidden>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
